metadata.name: Temptation #1/300
metadata.description: The limited collection features photography that was captured throughout Victor Abbate's life and tokenized on the Ethereum blockchain. Abbate has always found photography fascinating, when considering the idea of freezing a precious moment in time, for eternity. Photography can tell a story, good or bad. Photography transmits mood, pleasure or paranoia. What a photo communicates, depends on one's interpretation.
